{
  "stem": "17301.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a brick factory, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the buildings were made out of bricks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So, you know, we had some, someplace to hide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, we were like 50 or 60 of us in a small place, in a very tight little quarters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, they didn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So whatever food we brought with us, which was very rationed-- we rationalized the food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we lived on that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had, I was very lucky that one of the German soldiers that were with us came to look for us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he brought us bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he says, if you run out of it, he says, I'll be back tomorrow, which was very nice of him, and we appreciated it very much.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to backtrack a little bit because I forgot to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While the German were with us, before they took us away, one of the soldiers came to me and says, you know, I have a friend in Budapest and I would like to save you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like to take your sister and yourself and save you from whatever is coming, which I don't know what, I can't tell you anything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I'll, I'm going to hide you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, I really do appreciate it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I said, if you can hide-- if you can take my mother and my father, I'll go, otherwise I won't.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the decision, so I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's how we ended up in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't there are very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we must have been there about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after two weeks, they rounded up everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there with my, my aunt.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
